reviewText: GGW Canadian Bacon features several stunning young men who have no problem showing their maple leafs. If you like seeing the bacon of straight guys buy this dvd. simply yummy!

Even though not all of the guys were amazing to look at, the last one was the best! And there were many more French guys than I thought there would be. Overall, a nice addition to the GGW series, and I hope there is another edition of Canadian hunks soon!
